}}</ref>。

伊朗憲法中，[[巴哈伊教|巴哈伊教]]不屬於當局承認的少數宗教群體<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.fidh.org/IMG/pdf/ir0108a.pdf|title=Discrimination against religious minorities in IRAN|page=6|publisher=FIDH|accessdate=2008-08-03|archive-date=2006-10-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20061031221624/http://www.fidh.org/IMG/pdf/ir0108a.pdf|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，在伊朗被認為是叛教者<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.iranian.ws/iran_news/publish/article_26173.shtml |accessdate=2008-08-03 |title=Iran: Religious minority reports arson attacks |work=Persian Journal |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130610153003/http://www.iranian.ws/iran_news/publish/article_26173.shtml |archivedate=2013-06-10 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.abc.net.au/rn/talks/8.30/relrpt/stories/s892997.htm|title=Islam and apostasy|work=The Religion Report|publisher=ABC Radio National (Australia)|accessdate=2008-08-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111012073200/http://www.abc.net.au/rn/talks/8.30/relrpt/stories/s892997.htm|archive-date=2011-10-12|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，因為該教相信較[[穆罕默德|穆罕默德]]晚出生的先知[[巴哈歐拉|巴哈歐拉]]，違背伊斯蘭教中關於穆罕默德是最後一位被派往人類的使者的教義<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.clarionledger.com/apps/pbcs.dll/article?AID=/20080719/FEAT04/807190313/1022|title=Bahá'í believers know freedom and oppression|work=Clarion Ledger|accessdate=2008-08-03}} {{Dead link|date=September 2010|bot=H3llBot}}</ref>。有信奉[[巴哈伊教|巴哈伊教]]的學生因宗教被大學開除<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bahairights.org/2007/07/18/bahais-in-iran-deprived-of-their-education/|title=Baha’i children in Egypt not being admitted to schools because of their faith|work=Muslim Network for Bahá'í Rights|accessdate=2008-08-03|archive-date=2019-03-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190301013418/http://www.bahairights.org/2007/07/18/bahais-in-iran-deprived-of-their-education/|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.mideastyouth.com/2008/07/06/schools-out-for-the-bahais/ |title=School's Out for the Bahá'ís |accessdate=2008-08-03 |work=Mideast Youth |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20181221051917/https://www.mideastyouth.com/2008/07/06/schools-out-for-the-bahais/ |archivedate=2018-12-21 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://news.bahai.org/story/575|title=Confidential Iran memo exposes policy to deny Bahá'í students university education|work=Bahá'í World News Service|accessdate=2008-08-03|archive-date=2012-03-19|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/66GyjHHwS?url=http://news.bahai.org/story/575|dead-url=no}}</ref>，而巴哈伊教教育工作者必須放棄宗教信仰以獲得伊朗的大學教席。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.timeshighereducation.co.uk/story.asp?storyCode=203640&sectioncode=26|title=Segregation in Iran|work=Times Higher Education|accessdate=2008-08-03|publisher=TSL Education Ltd.|archive-date=2011-05-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110521172254/http://www.timeshighereducation.co.uk/story.asp?storyCode=203640&sectioncode=26|dead-url=no}}</ref>

